commit.title: Apply git conversion for line endings in bat files.
commit.message:
Apply git conversion for line endings in bat files.

Without this when one of these bat files is touched git will realise
that line ending conversion has not been done. Then the file will be
considered modified and it's a pain to get git to shut up about
it (you have to delete the eol= lines in gitattributes then run git
status, then you can undelete the lines).
